        "markerKey": "web-extension-book-twenty-one-the-dawn-of-the-iron-age-the-prophet-samuel-al-samu-il-the-reign-of-the-saintly-king-saul-talut:web-extension:4",
        "origin": "web-extension",
        "content": "<p> Deborah enlisted the help of the military commander Baraq, and they led the Children of Israel against the idolatrous Canaanites in the northern regions of Palestine (Judges, 4-5). Deborah’s campaign was very successful and renewed bonds of solidarity among the tribes in the face of oppression.     </p>",
