        "content": "<p> For Solomon in the Qur’ān, see 2:102; 4:54, 163; 6:84; 21:78-82; 27:15-44; 34:12-14; 38:30-40.        </p>",
        "sectionId": "web-extension-book-twenty-three-god-s-messenger-king-solomon-sulayman-his-unique-prophetic-powers-his-temple-his-reign"
